00:11:58.739 --> 00:11:59.779
Adiós.

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:03.080
Kang Min.

00:12:04.109 --> 00:12:05.249
Gracias por todo.

00:12:29.869 --> 00:12:30.909
¿Qué opinas?

00:12:31.509 --> 00:12:34.879
Bueno, está bonito.

00:12:35.009 --> 00:12:37.108
